title: Nice Cozy 1 bed 657 sq ft $980  Avail Now!
posting_body: ['Our 1 bedroom apartments are very spacious with 657 square feet.', ' This unit is great for entertaining as the kitchen faces the living room, and has a breakfast bar so you can converse with your company while cooking.', ' The kitchen includes plenty of cabinet, and counter space.', ' This kitchen also features a dishwasher, which makes the after dinner clean up a breeze.', ' Every unit has their own balcony/patio so you can relax outside on all of those nice days!', 'Our buildings are all controlled entry access.', "There is an on-site laundry in each building so you don't have to bring your laundry anywhere!", 'Single stall garages are also available so you can protect your vehicle from the weather.', ' These rent for $50.00 per month.', ' Our apartment community has a friendly, and professional management team, and a maintenance team that is available 24/7.', 'Do you like to take walks?', ' Our property is located right next to a walking path, and close to many businesses.', ' Highway 5 provides an easy commute to the cities.', ' Call or email us today to schedule a private showing!']
